- **Stale/broken archive link in canonical doctrine.** `docs/choir-doctrine.md` H031 says the older `mission-og-dolt-heresy-hard-cutover-v0.md` is superseded source material <ref_snippet file="/Users/wiz/go-choir/docs/choir-doctrine.md" lines="1171-1174" />, but the relative Markdown link points to `mission-og-dolt-heresy-hard-cutover-v0.md` with no `archive/` prefix; that file does not exist (it lives under `docs/archive/`). The same doc already uses the correct `archive/...` path at line 57 <ref_snippet file="/Users/wiz/go-choir/docs/choir-doctrine.md" lines="55-58" />. Fix line 1173 to `[mission-og-dolt-heresy-hard-cutover-v0.md](archive/mission-og-dolt-heresy-hard-cutover-v0.md)`.

