- **DoltPromotionAdapter comment still carries the 2026-07-07 false falsification.** The adapter comment at `dolt_promotion_adapter.go:18-22` states that branch-based candidate isolation requires sql-server mode <ref_snippet file="/Users/wiz/go-choir/internal/computerversion/dolt_promotion_adapter.go" lines="18-22" />. The mission doc correctly notes this must be corrected if the Phase A pinned-connection test passes <ref_snippet file="/Users/wiz/go-choir/docs/definitions/og-dolt-heresy-completion-2026-07-08.md" lines="553-555" />. Do not ship Phase D promotion code without updating or deleting this comment.

